---
source: tests/parser.rs
expression: "tree(r\"{a {b} c}\")"
---
ROOT@0..9
  PARAGRAPH@0..9
    GROUP@0..9
      L_BRACE@0..1 "{"
      WORD@1..2 "a"
      WHITESPACE@2..3 " "
      GROUP@3..6
        L_BRACE@3..4 "{"
        WORD@4..5 "b"
        R_BRACE@5..6 "}"
      WHITESPACE@6..7 " "
      WORD@7..8 "c"
      R_BRACE@8..9 "}"
